    },
    "has_children": false,
    "in_trash": false,
    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "A helicopter lands on the beach and then suddenly we’re overrun by cyclists. There is a race where they cycle up the coast without a route or use of GPS; just feeling out the path as they go. We watch them come careening down the grassy embankment and spin through the soft sand. The helicopter must have a film crew on it. Two stragglers come running around the rocks on the point, pushing their bikes - having taken the less ideal route around the point. ",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false,
            "code": false,
            "color": "default"
          },
          "plain_text": "A helicopter lands on the beach and then suddenly we’re overrun by cyclists. There is a race where they cycle up the coast without a route or use of GPS; just feeling out the path as they go. We watch them come careening down the grassy embankment and spin through the soft sand. The helicopter must have a film crew on it. Two stragglers come running around the rocks on the point, pushing their bikes - having taken the less ideal route around the point. ",
          "href": null
        }
      ],
      "color": "default"
