      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "There are people on the point watching and as the waves get better more people paddle out. At its most crowded there are eleven surfers in the water. The owner of Mdumbi backpackers paddles out through a gully and proceeds to choose some good waves and awkwardly rip a few backside turns on a Channel Islands performance board. ",
            "link": null
          },
