      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "I’m starving and make a second lunch of tuna mayo with Nandos peri peri sauce on Provitas - taking it down to the point to eat while I watch the waves. It’s looking smaller but every now and again the bigger sets sneak through the high tide and wrap in from behind the rocks. I’m on the fence about surfing. ",
            "link": null
