    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "I bump into Bas and Cam and they twist my arm. Before I know it I’ve suited up and am walking down with the Custard Queen to have another surf. Me and Cam jump into a gully at the top of the point and paddle into a couple but are too deep. Then everything just turns on and we’re trading bombs. ",
