          "plain_text": "The Custard Queen does such a good roundhouse with an effortless bounce off the foam. I do exclusively high lines and that classic roundhouse cutback. It gets dark and I get one more. On the first roundhouse and bobble a bit and hit the foam low down with my body fully extended. I continue standing dead straight and somehow don’t fall, and ride it all the way to the beach. ",
